Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.90,0:00:41.90,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眠れない夜に　聞いた物語が
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.28,0:00:46.66,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絵空事だとしたら…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.53,0:01:03.42,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠を知るより　快楽を求めて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.77,0:01:07.24,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今を悔やんでしまうのは
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.97,0:01:13.94,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心の深くに　住み着いた影から
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.19,0:01:17.79,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃げるためだとしたら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.49,0:01:23.53,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,それでも　あたしはあたしを
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.67,0:01:27.14,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛していられるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.35,0:01:31.00,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半分に割れた太陽が
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.26,0:01:33.34,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝を連れてきて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.53,0:01:38.49,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闇に慣れた神経を　じわり刺激する
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.85,0:01:43.68,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,置き忘れたの愛は　あえてそのままで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.16,0:01:48.55,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,シナリオの消えた物語は
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.65,0:01:53.82,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自由に　自由に　舵をとって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.16,0:02:00.32,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もっと　高くへ　舞い上がって
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.90,0:00:41.90,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在無法入眠的夜晚 聽到的那個故事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.28,0:00:46.66,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是天馬行空的妄想的話..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.53,0:01:03.42,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其探求永遠的奧秘 不如把握當下的歡樂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.77,0:01:07.24,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別讓此時此刻成為一生的悔恨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.97,0:01:13.94,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是為了逃避盤踞在內心深處的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.19,0:01:17.79,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那片黑影的話..
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.49,0:01:23.53,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算如此 我還能發自內心地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.67,0:01:27.14,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛著自己的話..
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.35,0:01:31.00,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分成兩半的太陽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.26,0:01:33.34,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶來了明媚清晨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.53,0:01:38.49,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微微刺激著已經習慣黑暗的神經
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.85,0:01:43.68,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把忘了帶走的愛原封不動地擺在那
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.16,0:01:48.55,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缺了劇本的故事就會..
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.65,0:01:53.82,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自由地 自由地  操起船舵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.16,0:02:00.32,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起飛向更高的地方去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.64,0:22:28.65,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ひとつだけ　叶うのなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.62,0:22:40.68,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君の手の中 揺れる小さな花でいたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.50,0:22:47.23,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,はじめてみる眩しいこの世界で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.71,0:22:52.65,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君ともしはぐれたとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.65,0:22:55.07,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,きっと　
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.16,0:23:05.77,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見つけだして
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.68,0:23:23.76,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目覚めたら　そばにいるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.46,0:23:31.63,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.64,0:22:28.65,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果只能實現一個願望的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.62,0:22:40.68,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想成為在你手中隨風搖曳的小花
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.50,0:22:47.23,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個陌生 而又炫目的世界裏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.71,0:22:52.65,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕和你走散了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.65,0:22:55.07,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.16,0:23:05.77,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.68,0:23:23.76,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒來的時候 就在你身邊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.46,0:23:31.63,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.09,0:02:14.89,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(940,600)}#12 「那個瞬間...我...」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.58,0:00:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天以來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.45,0:00:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在考慮這麼做是不是真的妥當
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.12,0:00:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就把禮彌託付給你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.70,0:00:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受那個噁心老爹之託來照顧禮彌的我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.82,0:00:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓禮彌獲得自由 與其說是開心..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.89,0:00:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實實際感受到的是肩上責任的沉重
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.82,0:02:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NO 味增湯裏放茄子是怎麼回事！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.56,0:02:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爺 那是青椒啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.26,0:02:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.72,0:02:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萌路 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.99,0:02:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.20,0:02:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禮彌吃的東西還真是很獨特了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.09,0:02:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是根據禮彌小姐的口味料理出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.44,0:02:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涼拌紫陽花葉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.08,0:02:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清炒紫陽花葉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.18,0:02:37.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫陽花葉清湯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.57,0:02:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊..會好吃嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.75,0:02:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我盡我所能去做了 不過..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.01,0:02:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依然痛感自己的能力有限
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.02,0:02:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都說了禮彌是素食主義者啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.84,0:02:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫陽花算是蔬菜嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.52,0:02:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我還是自己單獨吃比較好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.00,0:02:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.97,0:02:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是那個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.22,0:03:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爹麻煩你少吐槽兩句行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.43,0:03:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我只是對這些新奇的料理有些吃驚而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.65,0:03:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 請不要在意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.22,0:03:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿清
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.85,0:03:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿清！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.17,0:03:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺他偶爾會像這樣犯糊塗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.22,0:03:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果遇到的話就這麼做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.82,0:03:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊..是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.77,0:03:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多有擔待啊 禮彌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.95,0:03:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.32,0:03:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得已經很通情達理了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.96,0:03:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想除了爺爺之外大家應該都覺得蠻奇怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.32,0:03:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是沒有過問太多是因為大家都很體諒我們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.89,0:03:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到底 因為我們是一家人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.00,0:03:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要照顧一個人還真是辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.44,0:03:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更何況對方是個僵屍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.29,0:04:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.19,0:04:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.06,0:04:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼說呢..本想帶妳去其他更多的地方看看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.49,0:04:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.18,0:04:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我只能做到這點事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.45,0:04:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有這回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.41,0:04:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.87,0:04:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為在家裏的時候是沒法做這種事的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.17,0:04:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.78,0:04:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.36,0:04:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降谷同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.49,0:04:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天有煙火大會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.41,0:04:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 每年都有辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.13,0:04:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我是沒去過啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.45,0:04:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.65,0:05:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊 一直都是在自己的房間裏遠遠眺望
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.54,0:05:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總夢想著有一天能到現場去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.40,0:05:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.47,0:05:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.33,0:05:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正煙火大會也是晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.87,0:05:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會帶妳去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.31,0:05:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.79,0:05:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那為了不讓身體明天就腐爛 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.76,0:05:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會盡最大的努力的！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.99,0:05:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能一下子就腐爛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.44,0:05:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真那拿妳沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.33,0:05:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看個煙火就高興成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.56,0:05:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是小孩子嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.02,0:05:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是小孩子 有問題嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.81,0:05:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別忽然較真起來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.30,0:05:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維持禮彌身體的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.10,0:05:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防腐處理和防腐劑..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.35,0:05:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算查了各種資料也找不到有效的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.43,0:05:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實說來也是 阻止僵屍腐爛的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.82,0:05:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會有人以此為前提來做研究吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.49,0:06:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？你不上樓嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.05,0:06:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 有點事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.06,0:06:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠得住的只有爺爺了 可是..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.16,0:06:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼做才能保護好禮彌以及她的生活呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.37,0:06:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥 你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.85,0:06:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 有點事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.98,0:06:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 禮彌小姐不去上學嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.39,0:06:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上學？這個嘛..有點小勉強呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.47,0:06:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼又這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.17,0:06:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂健康上的理由啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.04,0:06:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去沒什麼問題啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.08,0:06:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去是這樣沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.63,0:06:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是身體內部有不少問題啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.59,0:06:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上我上學的時候她這麼對我說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.50,0:06:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上學嗎？真羨慕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.43,0:06:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.08,0:07:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生病的話 可以選擇早退或者隔日上學等很多方法的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.49,0:07:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些都行不通啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.40,0:07:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼禮彌小姐就要一整天都待在家裡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.50,0:07:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.03,0:07:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的生活對禮彌來說算得上普通的生活嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.78,0:07:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能算得上是一個普通的女孩子嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.76,0:07:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的人生 對我來說會不會過於沉重了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.14,0:07:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像回應了我的心情一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.99,0:07:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煙火大會也因一場大雨而泡湯了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.27,0:07:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中止嗎..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.04,0:07:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.03,0:07:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像..有點對不起妳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.73,0:07:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼降谷同學要道歉？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.54,0:07:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總這麼覺得..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.31,0:07:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明白你的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.10,0:07:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果..如果我還在的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.33,0:07:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明年再帶我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.23,0:08:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.70,0:08:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煙火大會泡湯也就意味著..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.25,0:08:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錯失了和一大群浴衣美女邂逅的大好機會！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.05,0:08:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這對於我這樣純情的高中生來講
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.58,0:08:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是人生的一個重大損失
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.11,0:08:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們怎麼認為？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.29,0:08:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,康孝啊 只要是女孩子誰都可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.25,0:08:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊..我又不是問你這個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.39,0:08:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是所謂的那個..怎麼說來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.03,0:08:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降谷 你也一樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.74,0:08:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.16,0:08:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定把散女的女生腦補成穿浴衣的樣子了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.16,0:08:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦 變態
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.70,0:08:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千紘 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.52,0:08:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 小狗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.07,0:08:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在發什麼呆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.00,0:08:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.62,0:08:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會又在想那個大小姐的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.53,0:08:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.49,0:09:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來嘛 跟姐姐傾訴一下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.46,0:09:00.00,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛..好痛..好痛啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.66,0:09:02.49,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛！話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.07,0:09:04.49,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前的那句未婚妻是怎麼回事啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.79,0:09:06.52,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是突然想說說而已~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.16,0:09:09.14,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛 對不起饒了我吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.64,0:09:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好呢..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.34,0:09:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的誰都行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.92,0:09:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是不否定啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.62,0:09:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煙火大會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.40,0:09:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那傢夥很期待著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.82,0:09:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.17,0:09:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來滿心想著要和千紘一起去的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.59,0:09:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.57,0:09:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們辦個小小的煙火大會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.23,0:09:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禮彌小姐..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.68,0:09:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓禮彌小姐幫忙實在沒法對哥交待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.50,0:09:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點程度沒事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.56,0:09:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不..可是..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.07,0:09:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.98,0:09:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是怎麼..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.70,0:09:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起啊 萌路妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.04,0:09:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.27,0:09:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降谷同學 歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.25,0:09:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥 回來得真早呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.56,0:09:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在幹什麼呀 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.49,0:09:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大白天的就在外頭打掃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.45,0:10:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那個可憐的掃帚..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.97,0:10:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.02,0:10:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是陰天 降谷同學擔心過頭了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.17,0:10:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.27,0:10:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.85,0:10:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後要好好去歇著哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.20,0:10:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.67,0:10:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我隨便問一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.54,0:10:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不我們自己辦一個煙火大會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.63,0:10:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煙火大會？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.27,0:10:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 今晚在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.75,0:10:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是火箭焰火的話 還是可以放一放的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.48,0:10:28.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,焰火我也好久沒有玩了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.33,0:10:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.29,0:10:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就決定了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.08,0:10:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狗說會借妳浴衣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.86,0:10:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳就穿穿看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.16,0:10:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且她說她會幫妳穿的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.25,0:10:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把氣氛弄得像樣一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.34,0:10:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狗小姐..她會來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.70,0:10:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,焰火也是她的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.38,0:10:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會把浴衣拿出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.28,0:10:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼等小狗來了 就交給她辦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.84,0:10:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要準備晚餐 所以..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.05,0:10:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 這裡我會收拾乾淨的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.00,0:10:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託妳了 那麼..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.58,0:11:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狗小姐..嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.51,0:11:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下午好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.15,0:11:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 蘭子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.45,0:11:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.04,0:11:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你們要放煙火？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.63,0:11:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 因為很不甘心大會被中止
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.55,0:11:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以至少我們自己來過一過癮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.27,0:11:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 小狗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.70,0:11:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 穿得很不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.82,0:11:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是萌路幫我穿的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.84,0:11:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 平時就穿得很習慣了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.88,0:11:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 禮彌呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.78,0:11:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在樓上哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.30,0:11:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禮彌？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.95,0:12:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊用纏帶勒住不會有事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.38,0:12:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 完全沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.29,0:12:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒不如請妳勒得越緊越好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.55,0:12:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.72,0:12:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狗小姐和降谷同學關係很好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.56,0:12:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好哦 畢竟是青梅竹馬嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.26,0:12:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他從以前開始就是個怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.77,0:12:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一開始雖然很火他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.78,0:12:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過優點也有很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.59,0:12:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我很珍惜他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.00,0:12:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.95,0:12:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般情況下他明明對煙火不會感興趣的說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.21,0:13:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一說要辦結果他馬上答應了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.33,0:13:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他很單純的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.85,0:13:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是認為這樣禮彌會高興
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.48,0:13:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不懂他這人到底是好人還是討厭鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.81,0:13:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過說到底還算是個好人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.17,0:13:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也蠻懂這個感覺的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.94,0:13:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 結束了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.22,0:13:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉過來看看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.74,0:13:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.95,0:13:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有半點不協調的感覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.68,0:13:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我眼前的這位女生居然是僵屍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.42,0:13:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實妳並沒有死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.48,0:13:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒那回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.99,0:13:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脈搏都沒有在跳了說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.20,0:13:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了肚子的傷之外都很正常吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.79,0:13:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不知道這種狀態能維持到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.03,0:13:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的時間沒有那麼寬裕..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.35,0:13:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體也不斷在受損..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.15,0:13:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？小狗小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.69,0:13:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 完全沒事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.79,0:13:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說是用紫陽花？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.29,0:13:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來那個很有效嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.40,0:13:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後千紘一定會想法子解決的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.16,0:14:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 說的也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.58,0:14:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能一直待在這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.59,0:14:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？不..我並沒有打算一直賴在這裡..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.72,0:14:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那妳要去其他地方嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.60,0:14:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我還沒..那個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.77,0:14:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還不清楚..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.71,0:14:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個..一直下去的話 會給大家添很多麻煩吧..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.81,0:14:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.09,0:14:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他會寂寞的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.73,0:14:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是..是這樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.98,0:14:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問..小狗小姐..那個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.79,0:14:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對降谷同學..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.85,0:14:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡哦 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.92,0:14:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.91,0:14:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？我啊..那個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.84,0:14:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不敢那麼得寸進尺..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.10,0:14:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好吧 我就一個人獨占千紘了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.93,0:14:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.16,0:14:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個..我覺得那樣就行了...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.19,0:15:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禮彌啊 難道妳是在照顧我的感受？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.90,0:15:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？什什什麼事啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.64,0:15:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的怎麼講呢..是人都看出來了啦禮彌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.59,0:15:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.25,0:15:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和禮彌是競爭對手啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.00,0:15:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.63,0:15:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我和降谷同學的關係沒有像妳這麼深
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.62,0:15:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降谷同學對我也只是出於對僵屍的喜好而已..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.00,0:15:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的受不了啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.39,0:15:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在顧忌什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.18,0:15:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才更要抓緊吧 既然沒剩多少時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.28,0:15:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了不留下遺憾才更要勇敢活一把
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.00,0:15:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然是女孩子的話！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.46,0:15:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小..狗..小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.03,0:15:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我已經死了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.48,0:15:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊 不擅長這種糾纏不清的狀況啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.33,0:15:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算禮彌喜歡千紘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.98,0:15:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.46,0:15:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而妳還是妳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.56,0:16:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是我不會輸而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.93,0:16:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以禮彌也要自己加油
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.88,0:16:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.90,0:16:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高興嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.43,0:16:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很高興哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.46,0:16:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我只能做到這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.98,0:16:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降谷同學 還真是經常在說對不起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.47,0:16:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為 這是..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.22,0:16:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.96,0:16:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能把我留在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.87,0:16:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是這樣我就已經滿足了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.93,0:16:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會無聊嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.13,0:17:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.20,0:17:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就沒什麼不滿嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.17,0:17:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.85,0:17:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能在這裡和降谷同學們一起生活本來就很新鮮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.55,0:17:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也很刺激
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.90,0:17:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在比起盛大的煙火..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.35,0:17:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得小巧的煙火更為美妙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.76,0:17:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.01,0:17:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡..歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.00,0:17:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問您怎麼了？大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.24,0:17:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要回學校
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.09,0:17:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此我來拿一些行李
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.63,0:17:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.30,0:17:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是..是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.96,0:17:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通知夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.14,0:17:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.58,0:18:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.54,0:18:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說妳要回學校？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.01,0:18:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我下定決心了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.59,0:18:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳還有什麼臉去那裡上學 那座屬於團一郎的學校
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.72,0:18:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您想要讓我退學嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.47,0:18:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 團一郎讓我什麼都別幹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.42,0:18:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我什麼都不會做的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.99,0:18:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨妳的便
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.05,0:18:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.43,0:18:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我真的什麼都不會做哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.05,0:18:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論擔心 照顧 還是幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.39,0:18:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做好覺悟了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.88,0:18:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那完事的話趕緊離開吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.42,0:18:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.00,0:19:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.94,0:19:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.21,0:19:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 降谷同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.44,0:19:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學校的事..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.62,0:19:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為妳想去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.21,0:19:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.37,0:19:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.92,0:19:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以哦 這點要求我也不好拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.77,0:19:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好高興
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.04,0:19:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為不上學的話 就不能算是一個普通的女孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.63,0:19:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點寂寞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.16,0:19:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳還是有不滿的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.22,0:19:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其說是不滿..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.54,0:19:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.97,0:19:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.53,0:19:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過跟我約好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.90,0:20:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要多加小心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.53,0:20:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.09,0:20:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護妳身體的這件事..和我一起努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.10,0:20:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.31,0:20:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.74,0:20:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.61,0:20:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以說個實話嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.26,0:20:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.69,0:20:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要盡可能長時間地讓妳保持現在這樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.16,0:20:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也可以說實話嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.31,0:20:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.02,0:20:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.54,0:20:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然不知何時會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.89,0:20:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要把能做的時候都盡情嘗試一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.09,0:20:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那就是女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.98,0:20:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.03,0:21:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒辦法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.43,0:21:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.23,0:21:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.28,0:21:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的幸福是禮彌的不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.91,0:21:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禮彌的幸福是我的不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.46,0:21:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.97,0:21:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我雖然知道..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.44,0:21:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但已經..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.01,0:21:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去學校的話果然還是啊..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.16,0:21:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那件外套裏塞一些乾冰比較好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.20,0:21:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是能穿外套的只有上下學路上呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.02,0:21:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且夏天也不能穿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.58,0:21:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 夏天穿外套其實也不奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.33,0:21:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼認為？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.85,0:21:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那個瞬間..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.09,0:21:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那個瞬間 我覺得我和禮彌一起平分了幸福和不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.86,0:21:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個瞬間..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.99,0:23:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.61,0:23:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散華禮彌 第十三話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.88,0:23:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本喵...也是僵屍是也...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.45,0:23:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家也要來哦萌路~
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.44,0:23:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.94,0:23:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很棒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.54,0:23:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個..沒有大家的話 我一個人是沒法做到這一步的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.54,0:24:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝之情難以自抑
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.14,0:24:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝大家
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.57,0:24:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很感謝..嘿嘿
